title: Fallout Nuka Break 1080p (Complete; original fan film, Red Star
description:
This is the complete Nuka Break series ripped from the official channels. Included are the following:

1. The Original Fan Film
2. The Red Star Fan Film
3. Season 1
4. Season 2
5. All official trailers

Season 1 is all one file. The source is the "Complete First Season" video on the Wayside Creations YouTube channel. Season 2 is separate files per episode, as there is no complete version yet. If there's enough demand, I can go back and separate out all of the Season 1 episodes into separate files, but for now I'm lazy, and really - who exactly is going to only watch one episode?

Everything is 1080p HD (albeit compressed YouTube crap... sorry) EXCEPT the Red Star trailers, which for some reason can't be ripped at their full 1080p resolution. They are 720p, however.

If you haven't already, go subscribe to their YouTube channel and give them a "Like" on Facebook. These guys are awesome.
